---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="About" description="About Jacob Allen — real estate investor, AI builder, entrepreneur.">
  <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-8">About</h1>

  <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-6 text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
    <p>
      I'm Jacob Allen. I invest in real estate, build with AI, and write about what I learn.
    </p>
    <p>
      My work sits at the intersection of physical assets and digital systems. On the real estate side,
      I focus on residential investment properties — finding deals, structuring financing, and building
      operations that run efficiently. On the technology side, I build AI-powered tools and workflows
      that give small operators the same advantages as institutional players.
    </p>
    <p>
      I believe the next generation of real estate operators will be defined by how well they integrate
      technology into their businesses. Not just CRMs and spreadsheets, but intelligent systems that
      analyze deals, manage operations, and surface the information that matters — automatically.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-50 pt-6">Philosophy</h2>
    <p>
      Build real things. Stay focused. Learn in public. The best way to grow is to do the work,
      document it honestly, and share what you find.
    </p>
    <p>
      I don't believe in shortcuts or hype. I believe in fundamentals — cash flow, equity, systems
      that compound. Whether it's a rental property or a piece of software, the same principles apply:
      solve a real problem, build it right, and let the results speak.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-50 pt-6">What I'm Focused On</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-zinc-400">
      <li>Residential real estate investing and operations</li>
      <li>AI-powered automation for small business operators</li>
      <li>Writing and sharing what I learn through my blog</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-zinc-800">
    <p class="text-zinc-400">
      Want to connect?
      <a href="/contact" class="text-amber-400 hover:underline">Get in touch</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
